Title: 'local' plugin crashed upon missing data on cluster
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1606201555
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0b1

The 'local' plugin crashed when configured on a cluster and no nodes sent data for a service.
This has been fixed, and the service now shows the generic "Item not found in monitoring data" message in that case.
